# Build context for quickstart/Dockerfile is the repo root. Keep it lean: the
# demo image only needs packages/core + quickstart/. Everything below is large
# or irrelevant to the build, and sending it would slow the first `up`.
.git
**/node_modules
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.venv
**/.venv
apps
pnpm-lock.yaml
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/*.egg-info
